{
  "_id": "novaMega1",
  "name": "Nova - Mega flow (all concerns)",
  "description": "Single flow that routes each file through the appropriate action: legacy codec cleanup (mpeg2/mpeg4/wmv3 -> H.264), oversized SDR HEVC capping (1080p>4Mbps, 4K>8Mbps), H.264 to HEVC at 1080p over 6Mbps, or audio hygiene (add English AAC stereo if missing). Files matching multiple concerns get the highest-priority video action with audio hygiene applied in the same ffmpeg invocation. Files that match nothing are skipped. Designed for the Windows RTX 3080 ad-hoc node; on a CPU-only worker, edit each Set Video Encoder node to disable hardware encoding.",
  "tags": "nova,video,audio,mega",
  "flowPlugins": [
